Net Positive Impact

Instead of offsetting and counteracting, every social enterprise we work with puts more back into communities and the planet than it takes to create their products.

Learn More

Why we do this

We believe in a world where every business can be a force for good. We curate the best products from brands with net-positive impact. That means every purchase you make sends out ripples of change. We champion brands that make a real difference in our world. There's nothing neutral about us.
